# 📊 Budget Tracker

A **clean, modern Django Budget Tracker** to manage your daily expenses, visualize spending, and track savings goals.

## ✨ Features

- User registration & login with modern glassmorphism UI
- Add, edit, delete expenses and income
- Categorize transactions
- Dynamic charts to visualize spending
- Dashboard showing monthly summaries
- Mobile-responsive clean design
- Default categories created on signup

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- Django
- TailwindCSS
- SQLite (local), PostgreSQL (production)

## 🛠️ Setup

1️⃣ Clone the repo:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/budget-tracker.git
cd budget-tracker

2️⃣ Create a virtual environment:
python -m venv env

source env/bin/activate  # On Windows: env\Scripts\activate
3️⃣ Install dependencies:


pip install -r requirements.txt
4️⃣ Apply migrations:
python manage.py migrate

5️⃣ Create superuser (optional):
python manage.py createsuperuser

6️⃣ Run locally:
python manage.py runserver
Visit: http://127.0.0.1:8000/